parameters:
\bustMsgExp[2, 3]\nc<Senpai>So you're telling me you accidentally entertained a very
special, extra-large client with our team members? This is
no joke!

\nc<Senpai>You should have checked properly before letting them in! One
wrong step and someone could have died, you know!

\nc<Senpai>And you! Report immediately if something happens! What do
you mean by slacking off like that!?

\nc<Senpai>I will make sure to report this incident properly. You all
clean up this room!

\nc<Saki>(Wow, she wasn't just being hard on me... She might actually
be quite reliable as an ally.)
\nc<Senpai>Saki, how long do you plan to lie there? Get up already!
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Ehh, are you taking it out on me...?

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Just write the report today and then you can go home. Make
sure to rest well at home and come to work tomorrow.

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Um... can't I take just one day off? I'm feeling really
messed up inside...

\bustMsgExp[2, 3]\nc<Senpai>No way. If you don't show up tomorrow, expect to be sent on
a forced assignment. Our organization is merciless to the
lower ranks.

\nc<Senpai>Don't complain to me. Besides, you were born with a sturdy
body even among succubi, so you'll be fine.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Ha, haah...(I don't remember being born a succubus
though...)
\nc<>Saki collapsed on the floor as soon as she got home...
